  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  aged under 65 years old

          -  receiving regular treatment

          -  HbA1c &lt; 8.0

          -  decreased HR response in deep breathing maneuver

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  heart disease

          -  neuro-musculo-skeletal diseases

          -  taking any medication that may affect HRV (such as α or β-blockers)
      </textblock>
